ely stagnant for a few decades may not be the most effective way to achieve=
 that ROI. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>And there are bigger structural issu=
es: it&#8217;s slower and more expensive to get fabs built here, we have a =
shortage of trained labor, and as </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/re=
direct/907e9e7e-77f3-472e-aee4-cb32ae98771b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7G=
