ext-decoration: underline;">Bill Gurley and Brad Gerstner pointed out on BG=
2</a><span>, our workforce may be too comfortable to stick with a company l=
ong enough and put in the long hours required to build technical expertise.=
  </span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That said, Biden has $39 billion to play wit=
