gh-paying jobs the same year that a Presidential election is occurring in w=
hich Arizona is a key battleground state. Yes, that does seem to be the cas=
e.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Either way, it&#8217;s an acknowledgment that techn=
ology is important, that the US needs to get back to building, and a step t=
