esulting crystal structure.</span></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: =
rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A=
 couple of weeks ago, they achieved the primary objective when its W-1 caps=
ule landed safely in the Utah desert. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55=
); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This week, Vard=
a announced that things had indeed gone really well. They successfully crys=
tallized ritonavir in microgravity. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">&#8220;That Varda=
&#8217;s ritonavir was created exactly as predicted, and remained stable th=
rough its return to Earth, is particularly promising,&#8221; Knapp wrote in=
 Forbes. &#8220;The version of the drug the company attempted is one of its=
 least stable forms.&#8221;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With the successful test r=
un under its belt, Varda is now a go to begin making drugs for pharma custo=
mers in space. Maybe even more importantly, as Delian explained, it paves t=
he path to Varda being &#8220;the first company to actually show that there=
&#8217;s value to atoms being moved back and forth from space.&#8221;</p><p=
 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">When the space supply chain is booming one day, you can tel=
l your grandkids (over tightbeam) that you were there at its birth.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><em><span>P.S. I almost wrote this in Tuesday&#8217;s piece o=
n </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/a1bb6832-2f30-4374-a776-c=
